Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This video is a special release provided to all of you by Shogakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When watching this video, please brighten the room and watch at a distance from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last week, you all explored Beika City and found many different stores, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:31.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,Introduce the city
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of stores were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A grocery store!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flower shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A supermarket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s family owns a liquor store, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called Kojima Liquors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, you have to pick a single store as your example.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find out what the store is selling, the plans of the owners, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it doesn't have to be a store, for example, a post office or a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:06.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask what kind of work they do, what is difficult about their work...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to ask a lot of different questions and then make a presentation to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:11.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sports Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, you can start discussing which store you're going to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, which store should we pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, let's go to a store\Nthat sells eel-over-rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we do, they can treat us with delicious food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.19,0:01:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, this one's on Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Where's mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing could happen.{Something like that may happen.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's typical Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.{DCTP: That's so like you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, where do you think we should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! What do you think, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm interested in that beauty salon\Nin front of the station, personally speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beauty salon, eh? The one in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unique, and moreover it will be very helpful for the development of us Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Unique and helpful for the development of the Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:27.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, it couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:34.78,Title,,0,0,0,,THE TARGET IS KOGORO!!\NTHE DETECTIVE BOYS' SECRET REPORT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since this is for class, I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, don't be shy, ask whatever you want.{don't hesitate to ask any questions.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's get straight to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In general, being a pro means receiving commissions from clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From investigative work to direct assistance{interventions}.{From investigation of infidelity to helping people escape at night.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, cases just keep happening around me.{DCTP: But for me, wherever I go, cases just seem to happen.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And {I have to unravel}unraveling criminals' tricks{tricks of criminals} falls to me instead of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm {the one }doing most of that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's yours, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, what kind of work are you the best at, or like the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Best at... Like the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that would be investigating bold{DCTP: sexy} young women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tons of free drinks while lazing around investigating at clubs is lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what I mean is, there is no place for preference in detective work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of young girls,\Nmy dad recently dated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then my mother severely scolded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said it was the scent of perfume on his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell your dad to go to a tempura restaurant after a date with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After sitting at the counter for an hour,\Nall his clothes will smell of nothing but oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, no wonder you're going to tempura restaurants so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's just that I really love tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uncle, you brought that upon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, since you're married,\Nwhy don't you live with your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet his wife kicked him out because he played around with young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I figured too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be irreconcilable differences.{Maybe it's a matter of differing values.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or it could be because of financial reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what is your annual income?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are these kids really elementary school students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, just answer their questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:01.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't joke with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I keep hanging around these little monsters...{If I don't get rid of these brats...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, is it already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you guys, I'm terribly sorry, but I have a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that? Did he just run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're going to shadow Detective Mouri to observe his actual working environment.{No, we'll follow Detective Mouri\Nand watch him in action.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep a close eye on him so he doesn't stop by a tempura restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, here comes the great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like ninjas in a manga{the ninja from the manga}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll notice them right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And send them away or shake them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Notice them already. Are you a detective or what?{DCTP: He is a detective, isn't he?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Station
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:52.32,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}On track one, the Tohto Loop Line will be arriving shortly for Shibahama station on the inner circle.{Inner or outer circle refers to the direction in which the train is moving. The inner circle moves in one direction and the outer circle in the opposite direction.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get off now, he'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he got off just before the doors closed, doesn't that mean he already noticed us?{But, he got off just as the doors closed. That means he's already noticed us!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,Numata Obstetrics and Gynecology
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:24.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He jumped off because he thought there was a 500 yen coin on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like it's just\Na game token or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd get off just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't follow him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's a 90%{kinda want to use 'ninety percent'} chance he'll take the next train, so we'll just have to wait for him at the next station.{DCTP-ish: No, eight or nine times out of ten he'll take the next train, so we'll just wait for him at the station.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he'll most likely\Nget on a car a bit further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:53.18,Signs,,0,0,0,,Midoridai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is one car further back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash can was a bit further down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he'd be embarrassed, so I figured he wouldn't get on the same car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same reaction as when missing the train at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is so clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a real detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I am a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.82,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masaya Murakami (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2-3-2-4-2-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like he's staking out that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nhis name is Murakami Masaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten days ago, a rich family asked him to investigate the life of their only daughter's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Keep running!{Like that! Come on, come on!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His acting skills are so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so that no one knows he's a detective, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recently read about this{ in a book}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The primary rule for a professional stakeout is to blend in with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Go, go! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\q2}His stupid behavior is no doubt deliberately planned\Nto be part of this Saturday park environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's truly a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those are his true colors.\NHe's a complete horse-racing fanatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he's not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, he's being cautious for some reason, and that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Right in front of my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we called the police right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we remembered the car's license plate number!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the criminals have been caught already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only that were true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that guy kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminals must want something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this was done by people from the finance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finance company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Murakami is an ordinary employee at a credit company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing of particular concern there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He gave out a loan as a favor to one of his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right, the subject of an investigation should be kept secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one responsible for the loan, right? And his friend disappeared.
Comment: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one responsible for the loan, right?
Comment: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his friend disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was pressured by the corrupt finance company to pay it back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just figured it out from what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:35.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's why he was being so cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was on stakeout,\NI caught a glimpse of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it was only a split second, they looked very much like those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know the name of this finance company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was going to figure that out next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you guys are going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Uncle, what do they want to achieve by kidnapping Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if they grab Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nthey won't get their money back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's the criminals' objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,One hour later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.39,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Etsuko Yano (24)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{She's already used }Using six different ATMs from two banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's definitely withdrawing a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One ATM can only withdraw up to 2 million yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's possible to withdraw at most 5 million yen per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she's most likely\Nwithdrawn about 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's probably what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girlfriend of the kidnapped Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Yano Etsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would Etsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scoundrels from the finance company are most likely using Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To force his girlfriend to pay off the loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should definitely be able to prepare that amount of cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't she gone to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as I can tell, she hasn't even consulted her father yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It's unfortunate, she's already worn out,}She's desperately fighting her anxiety, waiting for a call from the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seems to be looking behind her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminals probably told her to be wary of cars that might be following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the criminals noticed that Uncle was investigating Murakami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you guys to get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth is going to believe that someone is a detective if he's got five little brats with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! It's called camouflage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was renting this car part of the camouflage too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because he doesn't have his own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, cars are very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cost of maintaining a car is very high too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the reality of being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:43.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But, having her bring the money directly is very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:47.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could the criminals... be planning something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She turned around again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's saying something to the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already been following the taxi for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver might be getting suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As if they're trying to see\Nif our car will overtake them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happens if we pass them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll no longer raise suspicions,\Nbut we also can't follow them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's smart of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we really do let them find out, shadowing them will be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key to shadowing someone is to be unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even for a professional detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are exposed, then your cover will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's finally caught up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you call him, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Uncle was in the bank a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stepped out and called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked the Professor to use the spare criminal-tracking glasses to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, I can focus on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we can use the Professor's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're stopping! Is this their destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like they were only checking to see if this car really was following them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they stopped temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be even more suspicious\Nif we stayed here for no reason at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta, get out of the car quickly and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I really gotta go, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, Mitsuhiko, let's switch to the Professor's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara, stay here and keep me posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} sits up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've won this round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan. We've caught up to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn left at the intersection\Nof the fourth district of Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drive along the Okahata Highway toward Kochi and keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like in the movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the shadowing technique of a professional detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I really feel like I need to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's getting a little antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be getting close to her destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:31.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, let's turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys aren't going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the perfect time for the Detective Boys to show off their skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Courage and recklessness are not the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you guys really want to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do something without danger and within your capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something without danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Within our capabilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you requested, I brought the money with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let Masaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:20:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, we're going to use you as a hostage and collect ransom money from your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you? This isn't what you promised!{DCTP: we agreed on!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promises are made to be broken, young lady.{DCTP: Agreements are made to be broken, little lady.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you would do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promises are meant to be kept.{Agreements are made to be fulfilled/respected.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me teach you guys that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we're the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that was Izawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Yamamoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaneko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with their report on the record store{Audio 10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, Yoshida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Tsuburai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, and Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hear to your report, "Being a Detective is Fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When on a stakeout, Detective Mouri becomes part of the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible for his opponent to spot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is how a real professional operates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, while accompanying Detective Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We experienced first hand the\Nshadowing strategy used by professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our presentation on the activities of Uncle and Detective Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:41.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was a big hit with our teacher and classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:43.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our Keron{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} hasn't been home since the day before yesterday!
